{
  "chapter": 117,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述了“鬼童子”现身船上，为铁心兰与花无缺的婚礼带来礼乐。随后，白山君出现，竟将妻子白夫人推给白开心，引发闹剧。接着，鬼童子请来的神秘乐师团登船，其中不乏像祢十八、俞子牙这样自称名门后人的怪人。正当众人准备成礼时，“狂狮”铁战突然出现，他是铁心兰的父亲，性格火爆。铁战不仅对花无缺百般挑剔，还因哈哈儿和屠娇娇饿着了花无缺而大发雷霆。在萧女史的点拨下，铁战终于明白女儿的心意，但铁心兰与花无缺之间的情感纠葛仍未解决。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_feng_chao",
      "speaker_name": "陈凤超",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "晚辈等久慕前辈的大名，今日能一睹前辈风采，实是不胜之喜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_chen_feng_chao",
      "text": "你嘴里虽然这么说，心里只怕是想问我这老怪物为何到这里来吧？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_feng_chao",
      "speaker_name": "陈凤超",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_chen_feng_chao",
      "text": "其实你不问，我也要说的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_feng_chao",
      "speaker_name": "陈凤超",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_chen_feng_chao",
      "text": "我这次来，是为了两件事。第一件，我听说这位铁姑娘要成亲了，就特地去请了一班礼乐来，我可以保证那些人全都是一等一的好手，他们现在还没有到，铁姑娘就成礼了，岂非令我老头子脸上无光，所以，我只好请铁姑娘千万要等一等。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实我老头子和这位铁姑娘根本就不认得，我只不过是天生的好管闲事而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有一件事，说起来更有趣了。这次我无意中救了一个人。这人据说是个混蛋，但我老头子天生的怪脾气，最喜欢和混蛋交朋友。因为别人都不喜欢跟混蛋交朋友，我若也和别人一样，那么混蛋岂非就很可怜了么？一个人若很可怜，又怎能称做混蛋呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "前辈若喜欢和混蛋交朋友，那是再妙也没有的了，因为这里的混蛋，比别的地方所有的混蛋加起来还多十倍。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "看来这位就是‘损人不利己’白开心了，果然名不虚传，我老头子这次上船来，就是为了要找你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "我……找我？为……为什么？我既不吃人，也不赌钱，这些人里，实在没有比我更老实的了。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "其实也不是我老头子要找你，只不过我那混蛋朋友，跟你还有些手续未清，所以想跟你好好的谈谈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "快来吧，你这条没牙的老虎，难道真的已不敢见人了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这笔糊涂账，该怎么样才能算得清呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "算不清就慢慢算，反正你们是同靴的兄弟，还有什么话不好说呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "咱们都姓白，一笔写不出两个白字，千万莫要听信别人的挑拨离间，伤了我们白家兄弟的和气。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "一笔写不出两个白字，一只靴子怎么套得下两只脚呢？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "这位兄台说的其实也是实话，我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "实话？他这简直是在放屁，我和你老婆并没有什么……什么关系，我也并不想娶她，你来了正是再好也没有了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "岂有此理，贱内既已和兄台成亲，此后自然就是兄台的老婆了，小弟虽不才，但也知道朋友妻，不可戏，怎能调戏大嫂哩！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "你……你这是什么意思？你难道不想要回你自己的老婆？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "在下万万没有此意，这次在下到这里来，只不过是想和兄台办妥移交的手续而已，此后手续已清，谁也不得再有异议。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "我抢了你的老婆，你不想跟我拼命？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "在下非但全无拼命之意，而且还对兄台感激不尽……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "你……你……你感激？……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "在下享了她二十年的福，也该让兄台尝尝她的滋味了。她脾气虽然不好，醋性又大，虽然既不会烧饭，也不会理家。但有时偶然也会煮个蛋给兄台吃的，只不过盐稍微多放了些而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "你……你这死鬼，竟敢说老娘的坏话……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "大嫂莫要找错对象，在下现在已不是大嫂的丈夫了，这点还求大嫂千万莫要忘记才好。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但愿贤伉俪百年和好，白头到老，在下承两位的情，放了在下一条生路，日后必定要为两位立个长生祠，以示永生不忘大德。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不要我了，他居然不要我了，这是真的么……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "若不是真的就好了，只可惜他看来一点也不像假的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一定不是真的，他一定不是真心如此，我知道……我知道他现在一定难受得要发疯，我绝不能就这样让他走。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "我要去找我的丈夫都不行么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "你的丈夫就在这里，你还要到哪里去找？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "可是……我并不想嫁给他，这完全是被别人强迫的。",
      "tone": "委屈",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "你若不想嫁给他，方才为什么要羞答答的做出一副新娘子的模样来？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "小伙子，你能娶得到我们的铁大侠女做老婆，实在是你的运气。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "无论如何，你总算得到她做老婆了，你还有什么不开心呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "前辈，我……我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我知道你有很多话要问我，但现在不要着急，用不着多久，你什么事都会明白的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_zi_mei",
      "text": "你们用不着招待我喝酒，我向来不喝酒的，因为我个子太小，要喝酒一定喝不过别人．所以就索性不喝了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_feng_chao",
      "speaker_name": "陈凤超",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "既是如此，却不知前辈……",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_zi_mei",
      "text": "你是不是要问我喜欢什么？好，我告诉你，我只喜欢看女人脱光了翻筋斗，你们若想招待我，就翻几个筋斗给我看好了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们现在总该相信，我请来的这班吹鼓手，非但是天下第一，而且空前绝后，连唐明皇都没有这种耳福听到的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_feng_chao",
      "speaker_name": "陈凤超",
      "listener": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "text": "前辈们世外高人，不想今日竟……",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "speaker_name": "祢十八",
      "listener": "char_chen_feng_chao",
      "text": "你是不是姓曹？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_feng_chao",
      "speaker_name": "陈凤超",
      "listener": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "text": "晚辈陈凤超。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "speaker_name": "祢十八",
      "listener": "char_chen_feng_chao",
      "text": "姓陈的也不是好东西。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "text": "你就算恨姓曹的，姓陈的人又有什么关系？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "speaker_name": "祢十八",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "谁说没有关系？若不是陈宫放了曹操，我祖宗怎会死在曹操手里？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "慕容珊珊",
      "listener": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "text": "如此说来，前辈莫非南海烈士祢衡的后人么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "speaker_name": "祢十八",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "text": "不错，自蜀汉三国以来，传到我老人家已是第十八代了，所以我老人家就叫祢十八。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "慕容珊珊",
      "listener": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "text": "既是如此，前辈就不该忘了，陈宫到后来也是死在那奸贼曹阿瞒手里的，所以前辈和姓陈的本该敌忾同仇才是，若是自相残杀，岂非让姓曹的笑话？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "speaker_name": "祢十八",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "text": "不错，不是你提醒，我老人家倒忘了，你这女娃儿有意思。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_zi_ya",
      "speaker_name": "俞子牙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里可有姓钟的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_zi_ya",
      "speaker_name": "俞子牙",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "老朽俞子牙，昔日令祖子期先生，乃先祖平生惟一知音，高山流水传为千古佳话，今日你我相见，如蒙阁下不弃，但请阁下容老朽抚琴一曲。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_yu_zi_ya",
      "text": "前辈如有雅兴，在下洗耳恭听。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_yu_zi_ya",
      "text": "巍巍然如泰山！快哉，妙哉。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_yu_zi_ya",
      "text": "洋洋然如江河，妙哉，快哉。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_zi_ya",
      "speaker_name": "俞子牙",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "不想千古以下，钟氏仍有知音，老朽此曲，从此不为他人奏矣。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "慕容珊珊",
      "listener": "char_nan_guo_sheng",
      "text": "齐宣王好吹竽之声，必令三百人同吹，其中只怕有二百九十九人是比南郭先生吹得好的，前辈吹竽妙绝天下，怎么会是南郭先生的后人呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_guo_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "南郭生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "text": "姑娘只知道先祖滥竽充数，传为千古笑谈，却只知其一，不知其二。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "慕容珊珊",
      "listener": "char_nan_guo_sheng",
      "text": "晚辈愿闻其详。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_guo_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "南郭生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "text": "宣王死，泯王立，欲令三百人一一吹竽，先祖闻得后，就乘夜而逃，这段故事是人人都知道的，却不知先祖逃走之后，从此奋发图强，临死前已成为当代吹竽的第一高手，而且严戒后人，世世代代都不能不学吹竽，为的就是要洗刷‘南郭吹竽’这段笑话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_guo_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "南郭生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "text": "姑娘放眼天下，还有谁吹竽能比姓南郭的更好？",
      "tone": "自豪",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "慕容珊珊",
      "listener": "char_nan_guo_sheng",
      "text": "晚辈孤陋寡闻，失礼之处，还望前辈恕菲。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_da_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容大姑娘",
      "listener": "char_chen_feng_chao",
      "text": "时候已不早，大家也都很累了……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_feng_chao",
      "speaker_name": "陈凤超",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_da_gu_niang",
      "text": "你的意思我知道。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_feng_chao",
      "speaker_name": "陈凤超",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此刻礼乐俱已齐备，还是快些为这两对新人成礼吧，大家也好痛痛快快地喝几杯喜酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_chen_feng_chao",
      "text": "这话对极了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哈哈，常言道，春宵一刻值千金。咱们只顾着打岔，却忘了新人们正急着要入洞房哩！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行，现在还不行，还要等一等。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "难道前辈们也约了客人来观礼么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "不是客人，是主人。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "主人？主人不是都在这里么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "text": "老幺是不是跟你们一起来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "speaker_name": "祢十八",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "他不跟我们一起来，跟谁一起来？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "text": "他的人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "speaker_name": "祢十八",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "他的人在哪里，你为何不问他去？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "text": "我若知道他在哪里，还问个屁！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "speaker_name": "祢十八",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "我又怎会知道，我又不是他的老子。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "text": "你这人简直跟你那老祖宗是一样的臭脾气。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_guo_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "南郭生",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "你明知他的臭脾气，为何要问他，为何不问我呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_guo_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "南郭生",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "老幺本来和我们一起坐船来的，但他却嫌船走得太慢，所以就跳上岸，要一个人先赶来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_zi_ya",
      "speaker_name": "俞子牙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就叫欲速则不达。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他这火爆栗子的脾气，只怕到死也改不了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chui_xiao_nv_shi",
      "speaker_name": "吹箫女史",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以他近来的脚程，就算绕些远路，此刻也该到了，就只怕他又犯了老脾气，半路上又和人打了起来。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "韩笛子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是真打起来，那只怕再等三天三夜也来不及了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "前辈们的这位朋友，难道和人一动上手就没完没了的么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "不打得对方磕头求饶，他死也不肯罢手的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "莫非是他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "前辈们的这位朋友莫非是……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李大嘴、恶赌鬼，你们这些孙子王八蛋在哪里，快滚出来吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一点也不错，果然是这老疯子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个龟儿子一来，就更热闹了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhan",
      "text": "你这老疯子还没有死么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "铁战",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "你们这些孙子王八蛋还没有死，我怎么舍得先死？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "铁战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我倒忘了先看看你们这些孙子王八蛋究竟替我女儿找了个什么样的女婿，若是不合我的意，看我不把你们打扁才怪。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhan",
      "text": "我们替你找的这女婿，凭你这老疯子就算打锣也找不到的，包你满意。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhan",
      "text": "爹爹……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "铁战",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "好女儿莫要哭，老爸爸没有死，你该高兴才是，哭什么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "铁战",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "看来这小子长得倒还满像人样的，只不过……怎地连站都站不稳，莫非你们找的竟是个痨病鬼么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhan",
      "text": "这不是痨病，他这病只要有新出笼的包子就能治得好。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "铁战",
      "listener": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "text": "他这难道是饿病？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhan",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "铁战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁把我女婿饿成如此模样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼童子",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhan",
      "text": "除了你那老朋友还有谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhan",
      "text": "老……老朋友有话好说，何必动手呢！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "铁战",
      "listener": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "text": "什么好说歹说，你自己吃得一身肥肉，为什么将我女婿饿成这副模样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhan",
      "text": "铁兄有所不知，若非咱们饿他一饿，他只怕早就跑了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "铁战",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "跑？为什么要跑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhan",
      "text": "铁兄为何不问问他自己？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "铁战",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我问你，你为什么要跑？难道我女儿还配不上你这病鬼么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhan",
      "text": "爹爹，快放开他，这不关他的事。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "铁战",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "这究竟是怎么回事？……别的事我都不管，我只问你，你愿不愿意嫁给这小子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhan",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "铁战",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你现在怎地也变得扭扭捏捏起来了，这还有什么不好说的？愿意就愿意，不愿意就不愿意，只要你点点头，这小子就是你老公了，只要你摇摇头，我就立刻替你将这小子赶走。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "铁战",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我不要你开口，但你连头都不会动了么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhan",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "铁战",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "闭嘴，谁要你说话的？只要我女儿愿意，你就得娶她，我女儿若不愿意，你就得滚蛋！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_nv_shi",
      "speaker_name": "萧女史",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhan",
      "text": "女人家若是既不肯点头，也不肯摇头。那就是愿意了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "铁战",
      "listener": "char_xiao_nv_shi",
      "text": "不错，到底还是萧大姐懂得女儿家的意思……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 117,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    }
